{"tid":924701,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你有個咁既男朋友會點？","createTime":"2018-12-02T10:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:51:30.000Z","uid":32826,"like":1,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfddd74f2c1db03bf97a7ed59e58b103aa570a2","tid":924701,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"會睇141（被我發現話佢後繼續睇，睇得更叻會刪紀錄）<br />\n<br />\n賭馬、賭波、啤牌、麻雀樣樣岩<br />\n<br />\n就算應承我唔飲一個月結果（第二晚即出去一星期飲足7日）<br />\n<br />\n時不時就失蹤幾日...幾個鐘...<br />\n<br />\n明知我喊緊唔開心當聽唔到（最好盡快收線）<br />\n<br />\n其實我都好想分開，但我好似做唔到咁，最近仲大獲，我冇黎m都兩個月喇...<br />\n<br />\n今晚又失蹤啦...但我居然一滴眼淚都留唔出"},{"pid":"cae83f39aee5413a6b4c10ff3f8c97b036a15171","tid":924701,"uid":82500,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"明知佢係咁都比佢中出，唔底可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1464b2b59b716888923404ff19ff5de156a252b","tid":924701,"uid":69986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 講你"},{"pid":"ebca2b23e0a9e7e09a36d446dcce85d24c73e2b2","tid":924701,"uid":139176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"自己拎苦黎呻<br />\n爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09637ebffb0c50582d55b738e2887d31f5ca0662","tid":924701,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b1464b2b59b716888923404ff19ff5de156a252b","tid":924701,"uid":69986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 講你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"真係鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588a63dd3cbfb6256bd9bdd97f394153e6f2ce5d","tid":924701,"uid":157193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"岩架喇 男人唔壞 女人唔愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg